"次の５が引かれるまでサムマスターになる。\nその間1度だけ、ゲーム中好きな時に机や床に親指を置ける。サムマスターが親指を置いたら他の人はすぐに親指を同じように置かなくてはいけない。\n最後まで気づかなかった人が罰を受ける。" = "Be a Thumbmaster until the next 5 is drawn. \nThe Thumbmaster can place his or her thumb on the desk or floor whenever he or she wishes during the game, but only once during that time. As soon as the Thumbmaster places his thumb, the others must do the same. \nThe last person to place his/her thumb is punished.";

